OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FA number of water companies in England
OL,8,Fhave been repeatedly warned about
OL,9,Frisks to their water supplies,
OL,10,Fdocuments from regulators and the
OL,11,FGovernment show.
OL,13,FOfwat, the Environment Agency and the
OL,14,FEnvironment Department (Defra)
OL,15,Fnotified 11 companies about security
OL,16,Fof supply risk concerns last year as
OL,17,Fpart of the annual review of their
OL,18,Fwater resources management plans,
OL,19,Fwhich cover the period from 2020 to
OL,20,F2045.
