OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FIt comes after the Government promised
OL,8,Fto introduce MOTs for water firms in a
OL,9,Fbid to prevent repeats of the
OL,10,Fsituation that recently left thousands
OL,11,Fof South East Water customers in Kent
OL,12,Fand Sussex without supply.
OL,14,FSouth East Water blamed the recent
OL,15,Foutages on poor weather but the
OL,16,Fdocuments, uncovered by Watershed
OL,17,FInvestigations, show that regulators
OL,18,Fsent warnings for four years running
OL,19,Fabout the pressure on its system.
