OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FIn the most recent letter sent in
OL,8,FNovember last year, they said the
OL,9,Futility firm had "shown significant
OL,10,Fresilience concerns during dry weather
OL,11,Fwith supplies being restricted due to
OL,12,Fhigh demand."
OL,14,FThe other companies who were notified
OL,15,Fby regulators included Anglian Water,
OL,16,FCambridge Water, South Staffordshire
OL,17,FWater, Essex and Suffolk Water, and
OL,18,FAlbion Water.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
