OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FRegulators sent South West Water,
OL,8,FSouthern Water, South Staffordshire
OL,9,FWater and Portsmouth Water warnings
OL,10,Fover six consecutive years.
OL,12,FIn one letter, the officials told
OL,13,FSouthern Water that it had
OL,14,Fpersistently underperformed on its
OL,15,Fwater resources management plan
OL,16,Fdelivery, including leakage reduction,
OL,17,Fover the last six years.
OL,19,F"This has put both customer supply
OL,20,Fsecurity and the environment at
OL,21,Funacceptable risk," it read.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
