OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FTo South West Water, the regulators
OL,8,Fshared concerns over its management of
OL,9,Fhigh demand for water in the area,
OL,10,Fsaying this has "contributed to
OL,11,Foperational challenges and your
OL,12,Fability to meet customer demand during
OL,13,Fwarm, dry periods."
OL,15,FIt added: "This requires immediate
OL,16,Fadditional action to get customer
OL,17,Fdemand down."
