OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FThames Water was similarly warned that
OL,8,Ffalling behind on demand management
OL,9,Fwould increase the risk to security of
OL,10,Fsupply for customers in a dry year in
OL,11,Fthe short term, and to the firm
OL,12,Fveering offtrack on its long term
OL,13,Fambitions to reduce demand.
OL,15,FTo Anglian Water, and Essex and
OL,16,FSuffolk Water, regulators shared their
OL,17,Fconcerns that supply limits in some of
OL,18,Ftheir areas could hinder growth and
OL,19,Fsustainable development as potential
OL,20,Fnew users are turned down.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
