OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FJames Wallace, chief executive of
OL,8,FRiver Action, said: "This is yet more
OL,9,Fevidence that the UK is sleepwalking
OL,10,Ftowards running out of water.
OL,12,F"It sounds absurd in a rainy country,
OL,13,Fbut decades of under-investment and a
OL,14,Fprofit-first model have left our water
OL,15,Fsystem ` our lifeblood ` dangerously
OL,16,Ffragile."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
