OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FLast week, ministers outlined powers
OL,8,Fplanned for a new watchdog as part of
OL,9,Fa major regulatory shake-up that aims
OL,10,Fto turnaround the troubled sector.
OL,12,FUnder proposals published in the Water
OL,13,FWhite Paper, the Government said water
OL,14,Fcompanies will have to perform health
OL,15,Fchecks on their infrastructure to
OL,16,Fproactively identify crumbling pipes,
OL,17,Fpumps or issues at sewage treatment
OL,18,Fworks before they fail.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
