OL,3,CWater firms across South were
OL,4,Crepeatedly warned by regulator about
OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,FBut Water UK argued that the sector
OL,8,Fneeds the new regulator to be
OL,9,Foperating as soon as possible to
OL,10,Fensure flawed planning assumptions
OL,11,Faround water supply forecasts are
OL,12,Fcorrected.
OL,14,FA spokesperson said: "Water companies
OL,15,Fhave delivered the lowest level of
OL,16,Fleakage on record, but we know there's
OL,17,Fstill a lot more to do to meet the
OL,18,Fmost stretching regulatory targets
OL,19,Fever set.
