OL,5,Csupply risks
OL,7,F"We need the long-promised new
OL,8,Fregulator up and running and flawed
OL,9,Fplanning assumptions corrected as soon
OL,10,Fas possible."
OL,12,FAn Ofwat spokesperson said: "While
OL,13,Fthere has been progress, we have
OL,14,Freminded those companies that remain
OL,15,Foff track that they will be held to
OL,16,Faccount for any non-delivery of more
OL,17,Fresilient water supplies.
