OL,7,FA Defra spokesperson said: "Water
OL,8,Fsupply disruptions like those seen
OL,9,Frecently in the South East are
OL,10,Fentirely unacceptable.
OL,12,F"These failures cannot continue to
OL,13,Fhappen.
OL,15,F"That is why this Government's Water
OL,16,FWhite Paper sets out long-term,
OL,17,Fsystemic reforms that will prevent
OL,18,Fthese issues from happening again."
